{"tid":959570,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗仔白內障","createTime":"2018-12-28T16:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T04:35:52.000Z","uid":140580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f633c5234304901f3b1b3d8a948b01d90ab4785","tid":959570,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"我隻狗8歲幾<br />\n兩隻眼都有白內障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做手術的話一隻眼2.5-3萬 <br />\n成功率都高 但未必一定成功<br />\n做完要intensive地照顧佢一個月<br />\n有醫生話視力對狗嘅生活品質唔係好似人咁大影響<br />\n但係唔做又怕佢發炎同青光眼<br />\n而家好掙扎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人屋企狗狗試過？<br />\n做定唔做都分享吓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27a4c33131a57c55c117dcc8342fb9413cafbe6","tid":959570,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1b9fbc1f4d23ecbc94e4e5705687af6dc1bd564","tid":959570,"uid":198541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f633c5234304901f3b1b3d8a948b01d90ab4785","tid":959570,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"我隻狗8歲幾<br />\n兩隻眼都有白內障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做手術的話一隻眼2.5-3萬 <br />\n成功率都高 但未必一定成功<br />\n做完要intensive地照顧佢一個月<br />\n有醫生話視力對狗嘅生活品質唔係好似人咁大影響<br />\n但係唔做又怕佢發炎同青光眼<br />\n而家好掙扎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人屋企狗狗試過？<br />\n做定唔做都分享吓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"8歲梗係做"},{"pid":"88122195309f0294e0a276a81742481fbc9abf23","t